Class Car

java.lang.Object
Car
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Saab95, Volvo240
public abstract class Car
extends java.lang.Object
implements Movable
Collection of attributes and functionality of a car, with a position in a 2D space and a direction (angle). Attributes consist of amount of doors, color, engine power, current speed, model name, x position, y, position and direction angle in radians.
